{"id":232773991,"title":"法國酒同好請進","content":"從小農到大莊，從北到南全部都愛！\n\n不過...我很明顯是一個Burgundy lover\n有沒有法國酒愛好者 一起討論近期的愛酒呢？\n今天 這週 這個月有沒有喝到有趣的、厲害的、美好的酒呀？\n這裡不設限～～～～\n-\n2000 Leflaive Bienvenues Bâtard Montrachet\n不多說了..\n感人..只有感人\nhttps://i.imgur.com/0hYWhaB.jpg\n2018 Yann Bertrand Fleurie coup d’folie \n酵母味明顯 耐喝芳香的薄酒萊，同品牌的Morgon也很棒，更加厚實濃郁（我個人比較喜歡Fleurie啦）\nhttps://i.imgur.com/oalGen3.jpg\n2017Domaine de l’écu Nexus \n非常喜歡的羅亞爾河自然酒莊，喝完都拿來當裝飾😂這款Pinot Noir讓我覺得物超所值，有別於傳統布根地風味，不除渣，很純粹的果香再加上一點cloudy的感覺，有趣的選擇\nhttps://i.imgur.com/q5ZD6Wk.jpg\nNV Deutz Brut Classic\n口感很好，肥瘦均衡，鹹香細緻，酸度也漂亮\nhttps://i.imgur.com/HraLyx1.jpg\n2010 Robert Chevillon Nuits-Saint-Georges ‘Les Roncières‘\n喝過2014印象普通，但10年讓我很驚艷，非常溫柔甜美，一開瓶就好喝，但2小時後才真正開始綻放\nhttps://i.imgur.com/qQKKfuo.jpg\n2014 Francois Mikulski Meursault Genevrieres 1er Cru\n這瓶真的omg，純淨、酸度優雅，香氣又集中，太美好了～～～\nhttps://i.imgur.com/rI2li8n.jpg\n\n現在才發現有品酒版(´▽｀)\nBy Esther","excerpt":"從小農到大莊，從北到南全部都愛！，不過...我很明顯是一個Burgundy lover，有沒有法國酒愛好者 一起討論近期的愛酒呢？今天 這週 這個月有沒有喝到有趣的、厲害的、美好的酒呀？這裡不設限～～","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"23082c2f-c19d-456c-a805-1e6ac0a36c31","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-12-27T18:16:26.711Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-27T18:16:26.711Z","commentCount":6,"likeCount":21,"tags":[],"topics":["法國","酒","品酒板","品酒","葡萄酒"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"品酒","forumAlias":"alcohol","school":"淡江大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":21}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/0hYWhaB.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/oalGen3.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/q5ZD6Wk.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/HraLyx1.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/qQKKfuo.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/rI2li8n.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":